Products.RichDescription: Enjoyable healthy eating is all about choosing the best ingredients, that's why Real Foods Whole Grain Thins™ are the perfect crispbread to complement the yummy taste of your favourite toppings. Sorghum is an ancient grain that has been cultivated for thousands of years, originating in Egypt, but now grown all over the world. Sorghum is a gluten free whole grain,  which retains a majority of its nutrients making it a healthier choice than over processed or refined grains. Sorghum grains pop like popcorn, so are perfect for making sorghum cakes, a delicious and nutritious alternative to rice cakes, especially when combined with other whole grains, such as corn, brown rice, buckwheat and linseed to give a well-balanced, appetising grainy flavour.Sorghum Whole Grain Thins™ have a pleasant crisp, but not hard texture, with an enticing whole grain taste, making them the ideal crispbread base for toppings as simple as avocado and salsa, or more decadent smoked salmon, creamed cheese and cucumber, or for a sweet treat - fresh kiwi fruit and maple syrup. Sorghum Whole Grain Thins™ contain whole grains and are all natural, gluten and wheat free and non GMO, with no preservatives or anything unnatural added. Ideal for the whole family.
